text:
Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

Well Mr. BEE I want you to fly over to that flower and tell me what it is. The bumble bee searched the field for flowers and then flew back to the princess. Zach is the bee's name by the way.

He is a girl bee and has a sister named Zara. So the bee says anyway. The bee is full of it. Because his name is really Mr. Jeff Bee's son. Mr. Bee's son is very lazy and he doesn't want to work. That is how he ended up as a bee. But Mr. Bee's son is not lazy he is just a big baby. That is how he ended up being Mr. Bee's son in the first place. He was born that way.
